1
00:00:20,180 --> 00:00:26,020
=Manbo Destiny=

2
00:00:26,020 --> 00:00:27,980
=Episode 22=

3
00:00:43,123 --> 00:00:43,931
Are you okay?

4
00:00:44,854 --> 00:00:45,662
Baofan.

5
00:00:50,469 --> 00:00:51,370
Mengmeng? Is that you?

6
00:00:52,277 --> 00:00:53,431
Baofan, call an ambulance!

7
00:00:54,431 --> 00:00:55,238
Mengmeng.

8
00:00:56,623 --> 00:00:57,431
How could it be you?

9
00:01:32,315 --> 00:01:32,820
Mengmeng.

10
00:01:34,700 --> 00:01:35,860
Mengmeng, wake up!

11
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:45,900
I can't live without you.

12
00:01:48,554 --> 00:01:50,592
How could you leave me alone?

13
00:01:53,784 --> 00:01:54,669
Mengmeng.

14
00:01:55,669 --> 00:01:56,169
Boss.

15
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:57,284
Take care of yourself.

16
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:59,208
The First Princess has done her best.

17
00:02:00,015 --> 00:02:01,284
Let her go peacefully.

18
00:02:09,208 --> 00:02:10,592
How could this happen?

19
00:02:13,938 --> 00:02:15,169
I must go see my mother.

20
00:02:15,977 --> 00:02:16,592
Lin Ge.

21
00:02:16,977 --> 00:02:18,131
Calm down, Lin Ge.

22
00:02:42,807 --> 00:02:43,691
Mother.

23
00:02:44,760 --> 00:02:46,614
How could you strike
Guan Mengmeng so cruelly?

24
00:02:47,422 --> 00:02:48,768
You all go down first.

25
00:02:54,268 --> 00:02:55,230
Lin Ge.

26
00:02:55,384 --> 00:02:57,807
Is that how you speak to me?

27
00:02:58,730 --> 00:03:00,614
Blame that girl herself.

28
00:03:00,900 --> 00:03:03,153
If she hadn't insisted
on taking the bullet for Song Pai,

29
00:03:03,384 --> 00:03:05,230
would she even be lying
in a hospital bed now?

30
00:03:06,422 --> 00:03:07,730
How could you say that?

31
00:03:08,691 --> 00:03:10,230
My brother also calls you Mother.

32
00:03:10,768 --> 00:03:11,884
If something happens to him,

33
00:03:11,892 --> 00:03:13,084
would you rest easy?

34
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:18,739
Lin Ge, you really are foolish.

35
00:03:19,585 --> 00:03:20,431
Don't you understand?

36
00:03:21,277 --> 00:03:22,508
Only if Song Pai disappears,

37
00:03:22,508 --> 00:03:23,816
will the throne belong to you,

38
00:03:23,816 --> 00:03:25,046
belong to the two of us.

39
00:03:26,546 --> 00:03:27,662
In your eyes,

40
00:03:28,546 --> 00:03:29,816
even family can be sacrificed,

41
00:03:29,816 --> 00:03:30,316
right?

42
00:03:33,546 --> 00:03:36,162
Even Guan Mengmeng
taking a bullet for my brother,

43
00:03:38,623 --> 00:03:40,008
you consider it an accident?

44
00:03:40,393 --> 00:03:40,969
Right?

45
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:43,530
It's better if Guan Mengmeng dies.

46
00:03:44,376 --> 00:03:46,338
A man who lost his beloved

47
00:03:46,338 --> 00:03:48,223
can no longer be a threat.

48
00:03:48,225 --> 00:03:49,940
Then he will just be a walking corpse,

49
00:03:49,940 --> 00:03:50,978
a useless man.

50
00:03:51,517 --> 00:03:53,978
No one will be able to challenge us.

51
00:03:55,024 --> 00:03:55,563
Mother.

52
00:03:56,550 --> 00:03:57,550
You've really

53
00:03:58,704 --> 00:04:00,281
become unrecognizable.

54
00:04:02,204 --> 00:04:04,050
Now, for power,

55
00:04:05,857 --> 00:04:06,819
you stop at nothing,

56
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:09,092
even harming the innocent.

57
00:04:10,092 --> 00:04:10,938
Innocent?

58
00:04:13,977 --> 00:04:15,130
In the face of power,

59
00:04:15,515 --> 00:04:16,900
there are no innocent people.

60
00:04:17,823 --> 00:04:18,784
Remember this.

61
00:04:19,438 --> 00:04:21,553
Anyone who obstructs us

62
00:04:22,130 --> 00:04:23,130
is our enemy.

63
00:04:25,053 --> 00:04:26,361
The one who obstruct us

64
00:04:27,746 --> 00:04:29,553
is you.

65
00:04:43,707 --> 00:04:45,092
All these years,

66
00:04:45,900 --> 00:04:47,669
I've really been blind.

67
00:04:49,207 --> 00:04:52,438
I actually trusted you,
this poisonous woman.

68
00:04:53,823 --> 00:04:54,707
How dare you

69
00:04:55,515 --> 00:04:57,053
attempt to murder my son, Song Pai?

70
00:04:58,784 --> 00:04:59,977
Everything I did

71
00:05:00,515 --> 00:05:01,900
was for our kingdom.

72
00:05:02,746 --> 00:05:04,361
Once Song Pai ascends the throne,

73
00:05:04,430 --> 00:05:06,130
what authority
will the royal family have?

74
00:05:06,900 --> 00:05:08,323
You weaklings,

75
00:05:08,669 --> 00:05:10,400
how can you protect this country?

76
00:05:11,207 --> 00:05:12,400
But have you considered,

77
00:05:14,053 --> 00:05:15,092
if you lose your family,

78
00:05:16,207 --> 00:05:17,553
if you lose people's hearts,

79
00:05:18,669 --> 00:05:20,207
what meaning does this throne have?

80
00:05:21,092 --> 00:05:21,784
Family?

81
00:05:26,246 --> 00:05:28,130
Without the protection of power,

82
00:05:29,053 --> 00:05:32,246
you family members would have
long been reduced to ashes.

83
00:05:34,823 --> 00:05:36,400
Such a cruel woman,

84
00:05:37,707 --> 00:05:40,092
how could I allow you
to stay in the harem?

85
00:05:40,092 --> 00:05:40,746
Guards,

86
00:05:41,323 --> 00:05:41,900
take her away.

87
00:05:41,930 --> 00:05:43,823
- Lock her in the cell, pending trial.
- Wait.

88
00:05:45,284 --> 00:05:45,900
Father.

89
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:48,230
I know my mother committed
a grave mistake.

90
00:05:48,400 --> 00:05:48,938
But

91
00:05:49,707 --> 00:05:50,630
I beg you,

92
00:05:51,092 --> 00:05:52,515
for all the years of our bond,

93
00:05:52,977 --> 00:05:53,977
please spare her life.

94
00:05:55,053 --> 00:05:55,861
I am willing

95
00:05:58,592 --> 00:06:00,400
to give up my position as prince

96
00:06:00,790 --> 00:06:02,130
and bear her crime alongside her.

97
00:06:02,438 --> 00:06:03,630
Who told you to share it?

98
00:06:04,977 --> 00:06:05,669
Lin Ge.

99
00:06:06,592 --> 00:06:08,053
I am most disappointed in you,

100
00:06:08,977 --> 00:06:10,861
that you would betray me for Song Pai.

101
00:06:11,669 --> 00:06:12,592
Mother.

102
00:06:12,823 --> 00:06:13,746
What did you say?

103
00:06:14,630 --> 00:06:15,707
Quickly beg my father.

104
00:06:16,169 --> 00:06:17,015
Father.

105
00:06:17,323 --> 00:06:18,977
She was just confused for a moment.

106
00:06:19,207 --> 00:06:20,400
No need, Lin Ge.

107
00:06:21,553 --> 00:06:22,938
You're nothing but a coward.

108
00:06:23,669 --> 00:06:24,669
Without me,

109
00:06:25,361 --> 00:06:26,438
what are you?

110
00:06:26,938 --> 00:06:28,592
I have no son like you.

111
00:06:28,746 --> 00:06:29,284
Fine.

112
00:06:30,092 --> 00:06:31,053
All these years,

113
00:06:32,092 --> 00:06:33,400
I have tolerated you

114
00:06:34,207 --> 00:06:35,246
for Lin Ge.

115
00:06:35,938 --> 00:06:36,630
Today,

116
00:06:37,092 --> 00:06:38,207
right in front of him,

117
00:06:38,707 --> 00:06:40,784
I will expose your true face.

118
00:06:41,784 --> 00:06:43,361
Regarding the death of the late Queen,

119
00:06:43,760 --> 00:06:45,323
I have already investigated thoroughly.

120
00:07:20,682 --> 00:07:22,105
All these years,

121
00:07:23,451 --> 00:07:25,836
I have tried to be a tolerant husband,

122
00:07:25,836 --> 00:07:26,913
an understanding father,

123
00:07:26,913 --> 00:07:28,182
and a responsible king.

124
00:07:28,759 --> 00:07:29,490
But you

125
00:07:29,913 --> 00:07:31,297
still refuse to repent.

126
00:07:32,028 --> 00:07:34,259
And now, right in front of me,

127
00:07:34,259 --> 00:07:35,643
right under my eyes,

128
00:07:35,643 --> 00:07:37,028
you want to kill my son, Song Pai!

129
00:07:38,682 --> 00:07:39,913
Do you really think

130
00:07:40,220 --> 00:07:41,759
I don't care

131
00:07:42,720 --> 00:07:43,990
about the late Queen's death?

132
00:07:44,490 --> 00:07:46,567
She was my lawful wife.

133
00:07:47,951 --> 00:07:49,259
You were so cruel

134
00:07:50,259 --> 00:07:52,490
that you didn't give her medicine
when she was ill.

135
00:07:53,643 --> 00:07:55,413
You watched her life

136
00:07:55,413 --> 00:07:56,470
leave her body helplessly.

137
00:07:58,913 --> 00:07:59,643
Mother.

138
00:08:03,259 --> 00:08:03,874
Mother.

139
00:08:06,451 --> 00:08:07,259
Is what Father said

140
00:08:08,605 --> 00:08:09,874
all true?

141
00:08:10,874 --> 00:08:13,874
Was it you who killed the late Queen?

142
00:08:16,451 --> 00:08:17,336
Imperial Concubine.

143
00:08:18,220 --> 00:08:19,297
Give me the medicine.

144
00:08:30,490 --> 00:08:32,105
Who told her to block my path?

145
00:08:33,105 --> 00:08:34,797
Why should she be the Queen?

146
00:08:35,182 --> 00:08:37,682
She deserved to die.

147
00:08:37,682 --> 00:08:39,682
Take this evil Queen away.

148
00:08:39,913 --> 00:08:42,605
Even allowing her to live two more days
is punishment enough.

149
00:08:44,451 --> 00:08:47,220
Let go of me!

150
00:08:47,220 --> 00:08:52,413
I am the Queen!

151
00:09:29,374 --> 00:09:29,990
Lin Ge.

152
00:09:33,336 --> 00:09:36,451
I hope you will no longer
bear responsibility for anyone.

153
00:09:38,643 --> 00:09:39,913
Even your own mother.

154
00:09:44,797 --> 00:09:45,951
I hope

155
00:09:47,259 --> 00:09:49,643
neither of us will be shackled
by the past again.

156
00:10:43,490 --> 00:10:43,990
Mother.

157
00:10:46,682 --> 00:10:48,220
I have avenged you.

158
00:10:50,643 --> 00:10:52,105
The criminal who framed you

159
00:10:53,950 --> 00:10:55,951
has already received the punishment
she deserves.

160
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:01,143
I have not failed you.

161
00:11:04,143 --> 00:11:05,413
You can rest in peace.

162
00:11:21,500 --> 00:11:22,116
Mengmeng.

163
00:11:25,847 --> 00:11:26,731
I missed you so much.

164
00:11:33,885 --> 00:11:34,693
Fool.

165
00:11:35,924 --> 00:11:39,039
Didn't I tell you
I would definitely come back

166
00:11:39,500 --> 00:11:41,060
to stay with you and protect this land?

167
00:11:43,731 --> 00:11:44,500
Mengmeng.

168
00:11:45,077 --> 00:11:45,847
Mengmeng.

169
00:11:47,231 --> 00:11:48,193
Song Pai.

170
00:11:49,885 --> 00:11:51,000
You scared me.

171
00:11:53,193 --> 00:11:54,077
I'm fine.

172
00:11:55,577 --> 00:11:57,270
It was that oversized mascot costume

173
00:11:57,693 --> 00:11:58,885
that saved my life.

174
00:12:01,154 --> 00:12:03,231
I won't let you be in danger again.

175
00:12:04,731 --> 00:12:05,693
I'm not afraid of them.

176
00:12:07,039 --> 00:12:08,231
But I'm afraid.

177
00:12:11,847 --> 00:12:12,924
For my sake,

178
00:12:15,231 --> 00:12:17,500
I need you to stay away for a while.

179
00:12:21,154 --> 00:12:22,000
No.

180
00:12:23,039 --> 00:12:24,231
I'm afraid they will harm you.

181
00:12:24,231 --> 00:12:25,154
I promise you,

182
00:12:25,800 --> 00:12:27,608
I will protect myself well.

183
00:12:30,262 --> 00:12:31,646
After everything is over,

184
00:12:33,608 --> 00:12:34,877
I want you to come back to me.

185
00:12:37,954 --> 00:12:38,800
Do you understand?

186
00:12:40,069 --> 00:12:40,992
Wait for me at home.

187
00:12:42,646 --> 00:12:43,608
I will wait for you.

188
00:12:47,223 --> 00:12:49,531
No matter what, I will never
let you leave me again.

189
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:05,884
Recently, the news
about First Prince Song Pai

190
00:13:05,909 --> 00:13:08,240
and the First Princess Guan Mengmeng's
contractual marriage

191
00:13:08,250 --> 00:13:09,575
has already been widely leaked.

192
00:13:09,575 --> 00:13:12,614
There is even a prenuptial agreement
proving its authenticity.

193
00:13:12,845 --> 00:13:14,460
It has sparked public outrage.

194
00:13:15,037 --> 00:13:16,883
Negative emotions continue to spread.

195
00:13:27,691 --> 00:13:28,768
You must help me.

196
00:13:33,620 --> 00:13:35,614
Song Pai advocates
his mother's political ideals.

197
00:13:35,614 --> 00:13:36,980
The Reformists is growing stronger.

198
00:13:36,990 --> 00:13:38,383
If he succeeds,

199
00:13:38,383 --> 00:13:40,306
the Conservatives
will be completely destroyed.

200
00:13:40,845 --> 00:13:41,691
By then,

201
00:13:41,691 --> 00:13:42,845
our families

202
00:13:42,845 --> 00:13:44,460
will have nothing left.

203
00:13:46,229 --> 00:13:47,498
It's not that serious, right?

204
00:13:48,614 --> 00:13:50,960
Destroying our two great families

205
00:13:51,306 --> 00:13:52,652
is wishful thinking.

206
00:13:55,152 --> 00:13:56,191
But Queen,

207
00:13:58,114 --> 00:13:59,575
murdering the First Prince

208
00:13:59,575 --> 00:14:00,998
is a capital crime.

209
00:14:01,922 --> 00:14:03,922
I truly can't help you.

210
00:14:04,729 --> 00:14:06,229
Sorry, my apologies.

211
00:14:07,345 --> 00:14:08,114
Stop right there!

212
00:14:11,114 --> 00:14:13,383
Fine, go ahead, leave.

213
00:14:13,768 --> 00:14:15,883
I will immediately report
that matter to the King.

214
00:14:27,220 --> 00:14:29,700
♪I do this for you♪

215
00:14:30,100 --> 00:14:32,340
♪The love is fake♪

216
00:14:32,740 --> 00:14:35,100
♪The love is true♪

217
00:14:35,900 --> 00:14:37,980
♪For you♪
